OL,3,CWork to remove controversial 'wiggly
OL,4,Cline' road markings to start
OL,6,FWork to remove Clevedon's
OL,7,Fcontroversial 'wiggly lines' road
OL,8,Fmarkings will start in mid-February.
OL,10,FNorth Somerset Council will remove the
OL,11,Fmarkings from The Beach - described by
OL,12,Fthe RAC as one of the "most bizarre"
OL,13,Froad schemes it has ever seen - over
OL,14,Fthe next 12 weeks.
OL,16,FThe project, which is due to finish by
OL,17,FMay half-term, will cost #425,000 and
OL,18,Fresult in sections of the seafront
OL,19,Froad being closed temporarily.
