OL,3,CWork to remove controversial 'wiggly
OL,4,Cline' road markings to start
OL,6,FIt will mark the conclusion of a three-
OL,7,Fyear debacle in which the council has
OL,8,Ffaced public outcry over its "yellow
OL,9,Fbrick road" markings.
OL,11,FHannah Young, who is the council's
OL,12,Fexecutive member for highways,
OL,13,Fexplained the changes: "We plan to
OL,14,Freinstate the sea facing parking,
OL,15,Freplace the two-way cycle path with a
OL,16,Fsingle contraflow cycle path and
OL,17,Fadjust the roundabout to a traditional
OL,18,Flayout which is enabled by changing
OL,19,Fthe position of the cycle lane.
