OL,6,F"We will be formally publicising the
OL,7,Fworks this week and will provide
OL,8,Fdirectly affected local businesses and
OL,9,Fresidents along the seafront with more
OL,10,Fdetails shortly."
OL,12,FAs part of the revised layout, The
OL,13,FBeach will remain a one-way system but
OL,14,Fwith improved road markings and
OL,15,Fsignage.
OL,17,FThe original changes to the road cost
OL,18,Fover #1 million, as the scheme went
OL,19,Fover budget.
