OL,3,CWork to remove controversial 'wiggly
OL,4,Cline' road markings to start
OL,6,FNow, in order to fund the #425,000
OL,7,Frequired for repairs, the council
OL,8,Fexecutive voted in March to redirect
OL,9,F#50,000 which had been earmarked for
OL,10,Frepairing the slipway and another
OL,11,Funallocated #21,000 from the Great
OL,12,FLakes project.
OL,14,FAdditional funding will come from
OL,15,Fsection 106 money from developers and
OL,16,Flocal transport plan funding.
OL,18,FThe council is also taking #153,000
OL,19,Fout of its capital and revenue
OL,20,Freserves.
